\c 54
\s Jehovha ane rudo rukuru neZiyoni
\p
\v 1 "Imba, iwe ngomwa, iwe usina kubereka;muka nokuimba , udanidzirise, iwe usina kumbosununguka; nokuti vana vouri oga vazhinji kukunda vana vomukadzi akawanikwa."Ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha."
\p
\v 2 Kurisa nzvimbo yetende rako, ngavatatamure maketeni eugaro hwako; usarega, urebese mabote ako, usimbise mbambo dzako.
\p
\v 3 "Nokuti uchapararira kuruoko rworudyi nokuruboshwe;vana vako vachagara nhaka yavahedheni,vaite matongo agarwe.
\v 4 Usatya , nokuti haunganyadziswi;uye usakanganiswa, nokuti haungavi nenyadzi; nokuti uchakanganwa kunyara kwohumhandara hwako, haungazorangariri kuzvidzwa kwohuchirikadzi hwako.
\v 5 Nokuti Muiti wako ndiye murume wako, Jehovha wehondo ndiro zita rake; Mudzikunuri wako ndiye Mutsvene waIsiraeri, iye achanzi Mwari wenyika yose.
\p
\v 6 "Nokuti Jehovha akakudana somukadzi, akasiyiwa ane shungu pamweya, somukadzi akawanikwa achiri muduku ndokuzorambwa ndizvo zvinotaura Mwari wako.
\v 7Kwechinguvana,ndakakusiya , asi nenyasha huru ndichakuunganidza.
\v 8 Nehasha dzakapupuma, ndakakuvanzira chiso changu kwechinguvana ; asi nohunyoro husingaperi ndichakunzwira nyasha , ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha Mudzikunuri wako.
\v 9 Nokuti izvi zvakaita \add se\add*mvura yaNoa kwandiri; nokuti \add sezva\add*ndakapika kuti mvura yaNoa haingazodarikizve napanyika, saizvozvo ndakapika kuti handichazokutsamwiri, kana kukutuka.
\v 10 Nokuti makomo achabva, nezvikomo zvibviswe, asi hunyoro hwangu haungabvi kwauri, Kana sungano yangu yorugare haingabviswi ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha ane nyasha newe.
\s Jerusarema idzva
\p
\v 11 "Haiwa, iwe mutambudziki, wakaposerwa \add nedutu\add* remhepo, usina kunyaradzwa, tarira, ndichateya mabwe ako namavara akanaka, ndichateya nheyo dzako \add namabwe\add* esafiri.
\v 12 Ndichaita shongwe dzako namabwe anovaima, namasuo ako namabwe anopenya, nomuganho wako wose namabwe anokosha.
\v 13 Vana vako vose vachadzidziswa naJehovha, rugare rwavana vako ruchava rukuru.
\v 14 Uchasimbiswa mukururama; uchava kure nokumanikidzwa, nokuti hauna chaungatya, uye kure nezvinotyisa, nokuti hakuna chingasvika kwauri.
\v 15 Tarira, kunyange vakakuvamba, hazvingabvi kwandiri; ani naani anokuvamba achaparadzwa nokuda kwako.
\v 16 Tarira, ndini ndakasika mupfuri anopfutidza moto wamazimbe, ndokuita nhumbi yakakwanira basa rake; ndakasika muparadzi, kuti aparadze.
\v 17 Hakuna nhumbi inoumbwa kuzorwa newe ingaita chinhu; rurimi rumwe norumwe runokukwirira pakutongwa ruchakundwa newe. Ndiyo nhaka yavaranda vaJehovha, nokururama kwavo kwandiri ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha."
